{"tid":2025927,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳建強：嬉笑怒罵節目非不可以做 要拿捏是否準確持平","createTime":"2020-05-20T14:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T15:06:59.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"35115aa5ec761939ddbe137b4e249955f4c6ba9e","tid":2025927,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"陳建強：嬉笑怒罵節目非不可以做 要拿捏是否準確持平<br />\n2020-05-20 HKT 22:33<br />\n<br />\n港台節目顧問委員會主席陳建強認為，嬉笑怒罵節目不是不可以做，但總編輯和團隊，一定要拿捏是否做到準確持平。<br />\n<br />\n有民主派議員疑商經局、通訊局及顧委會 聯成一線向港台施壓，擔心《頭條新聞》會永久消失；有建制派議員認為 通訊局向港台發出警告正確，認為港台管治出現問題，政府要全面檢視及檢討。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527324-20200520.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527324-20200520.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krFIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=a72f3de0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527324-20200520.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4b34148e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527324-20200520.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好肯定嬉笑怒罵地嘲諷泛民本土港獨就一定係準確持平</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"03d32a978fbfd059519668c1c5f68699f20a14f4","tid":2025927,"uid":52638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"嬉笑怒駡地持平<br />\n同有中國特色嘅社會主義一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a412bd40b4de68748d23efa5acc26b5275b3fb","tid":2025927,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:04:54.000Z","msg":"欲加之罪，帶頭分化但係又話其他人仇恨警隊"},{"pid":"fbc851ebdce2afc8e5b17a247d49e915fe6e5f5f","tid":2025927,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:06:59.000Z","msg":"持平 ：警察唔係個個偷冰"}]}